snippet.title: FNAF Plus #6(B) - Help Wanted
snippet.description:
Teaser video #6(B) - Help Wanted
Mirror: https://streamable.com/bu0v83
Official Account: https://twitter.com/FNAFPLUS

. . . . .

LOCAL PIZZERIA AT THE CENTER OF CONTROVERSY YET AGAIN.

Freddy Fazbear's Pizza is back in the public eye this year, but not for the reasons they had hoped, as the small business was dragged into a torrent of anger and suspicion due to alleged ties to the disappearance of a local high school student on October 9th. The young teen, known to friends as a hobbyist filmmaker and described by some as a "quiet but well-mannered soul", was reported missing the morning after leaving home to "meet up with someone for a new project" that, according to family, involved the restaurant's infamous string of incidents and general dark reputation.

When pressed for comment, an intern at the establishment stated: "We really had nothing to do with it! Our surveillance cameras showed no one entering or leaving (the restaurant) during that night..." An answer that did nothing but grow more suspicion, as access to the aforementioned footage was immediately denied to the public.

Town residents were further outraged the following week, as they found multiple job flyers for the restaurant being left at their doorsteps.

. . . . .
